componentId.description: ID of the primary component in the packaged component.

componentName.description: Name of the primary component in the packaged component.

componentType.description: Component type of the primary component in the packaged component.

currentVersion.description: Packaged component version of the component that is currently released in this integration pack.

deleted.description: If true, the packaged component will be removed from the integration pack in the next release.

latestVersion.description: Latest packaged component version of the component that is available to be added to this integration pack.

pendingVersion.description: Packaged component version of the component that will be included in the next release of this integration pack.
